entry.title: ind3p3nd3nt/RDPWraper
entry.summary: Easy and automatic termsrv.dll patcher for Windows 10 1909 version 18363.959 - with updated ini file. To install make a "RDP Wrapper" directory in Program Files, Copy all those files inside then disconnect internet and in Command Prompt window execute "RDPWinst.exe -i"
